1
00:00:53,287 --> 00:00:54,667
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">There we go...</font>

2
00:00:56,287 --> 00:00:59,197
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Make sure you listen to your uncle.</font>

3
00:00:59,197 --> 00:01:00,367
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah.</font>

4
00:01:00,367 --> 00:01:02,247
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Do you have your handkerchief? Your ticket?</font>

5
00:01:02,247 --> 00:01:04,367
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">A nice pair of shoes?</font>

6
00:01:04,367 --> 00:01:05,787
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Wait, don't tell me that's everything?</font>

7
00:01:05,787 --> 00:01:08,047
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's fine. I made sure I packed the black ones.</font>

8
00:01:15,687 --> 00:01:19,157
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Jeez. I've been going there every year, so I'll be all right.</font>

9
00:02:04,567 --> 00:02:12,907
<font face="Constantia" size="110" color="#e4f0fb">{\an8}To the Forest of Firefly Lights</font>

10
00:02:19,827 --> 00:02:21,997
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>which was said to be where spirits lived.</i></font>

11
00:02:24,867 --> 00:02:27,557
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>After running around searching for an exit</i></font>

12
00:02:27,557 --> 00:02:29,627
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>I became so tired I couldn't move.</i></font>

13
00:02:30,567 --> 00:02:35,147
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>When I started crying from fear and loneliness,</i></font>

14
00:03:08,277 --> 00:03:11,667
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's a person! I'm saved!</font>

15
00:03:24,717 --> 00:03:26,187
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">S-Sorry.</font>

16
00:04:57,737 --> 00:04:59,197
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Grab the other end.</font>

17
00:05:00,237 --> 00:05:01,347
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You're lost, aren't you?</font>

18
00:05:02,767 --> 00:05:04,467
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'll lead you out of the forest.</font>

19
00:05:32,007 --> 00:05:34,457
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's just like going on a date!</font>

20
00:05:35,027 --> 00:05:36,997
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Not a very romantic one...</font>

21
00:05:59,717 --> 00:06:00,427
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Bye.</font>

22
00:06:12,387 --> 00:06:14,977
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Set foot within, and you'll lose your way and be lost forever.</font>

23
00:06:16,697 --> 00:06:17,947
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You shouldn't come here.</font>

24
00:06:18,987 --> 00:06:21,117
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That's what the villagers say, right?</font>

25
00:06:49,037 --> 00:06:52,707
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Anyway, I'll be back tomorrow with a thank-you present!</font>

26
00:07:13,737 --> 00:07:14,537
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hotaru!</font>

27
00:07:14,537 --> 00:07:16,327
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ah, Uncle!</font>

28
00:07:37,727 --> 00:07:38,647
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Uncle.</font>

29
00:07:38,647 --> 00:07:39,627
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Huh?</font>

30
00:07:40,317 --> 00:07:43,107
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is it true that there are spirits living in that forest?</font>

31
00:07:59,357 --> 00:08:05,357
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">In the end, I never met any, but I had the feeling I'd occasionally spot something from the corner of my eye.</font>

32
00:08:06,747 --> 00:08:11,417
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">On summer nights, you could hear the sounds of the river coming from the forest.{*TLC hayashi?}</font>

33
00:08:23,277 --> 00:08:25,957
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">So then, whose festival could it have been?</font>

34
00:09:42,687 --> 00:09:43,567
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You came.</font>

35
00:09:46,117 --> 00:09:48,387
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I didn't think you'd really come back.</font>

36
00:10:12,997 --> 00:10:14,187
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Don't worry.</font>

37
00:10:14,647 --> 00:10:16,097
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'll see you out of here again.</font>

38
00:11:25,237 --> 00:11:26,607
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is that so?</font>

39
00:11:27,247 --> 00:11:28,637
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Human child.</font>

40
00:11:29,157 --> 00:11:32,027
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Please don't touch Gin's skin.</font>

41
00:11:33,107 --> 00:11:38,267
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If you do, I'll eat you!</font>

42
00:11:43,657 --> 00:11:45,537
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Oh! Is that a fox?</font>

43
00:11:49,407 --> 00:11:50,527
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">He's another one of the spirits.</font>

44
00:11:52,087 --> 00:11:55,457
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">He transforms to scare people, but he's all bark and no bite.{He transforms to scare people, but he's actually cowardly and a good guy.}</font>

45
00:12:16,317 --> 00:12:18,287
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Why do you wear a mask?</font>

46
00:12:53,877 --> 00:12:55,427
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Over here, over here!</font>

47
00:12:56,657 --> 00:12:58,497
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's better over there.</font>

48
00:13:13,747 --> 00:13:15,387
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Even though it was silly,</i></font>

49
00:13:42,117 --> 00:13:45,137
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Did Gin fall asleep?</font>

50
00:14:13,327 --> 00:14:15,607
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ah, sorry!</font>

51
00:14:15,607 --> 00:14:17,007
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ouch!</font>

52
00:14:22,127 --> 00:14:24,507
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm sorry, but</font>

53
00:14:33,717 --> 00:14:35,577
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Why are you wearing that mask?</font>

54
00:14:36,577 --> 00:14:38,397
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If I don't wear this mask,</font>

55
00:14:39,087 --> 00:14:40,797
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I don't look like a spirit, do I?</font>

56
00:14:52,637 --> 00:14:53,887
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You're weird.</font>

57
00:15:02,297 --> 00:15:03,677
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Um, Gin.</font>

58
00:15:05,127 --> 00:15:07,287
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I won't be able</font>

59
00:15:08,067 --> 00:15:09,967
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">to come here tomorrow.</font>

60
00:15:17,177 --> 00:15:20,767
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">So I have to go home tomorrow.</font>

61
00:15:27,007 --> 00:15:28,447
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Will you be able to come again next year?</font>

62
00:15:32,617 --> 00:15:33,457
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah!</font>

63
00:15:36,927 --> 00:15:38,447
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>This is how summer</i></font>

64
00:15:39,627 --> 00:15:42,427
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>became something I looked forward to.</i></font>

65
00:15:59,057 --> 00:16:00,827
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's cold!</font>

66
00:16:41,457 --> 00:16:45,117
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Please don't touch him, human child.</font>

67
00:16:46,737 --> 00:16:47,377
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yes.</font>

68
00:17:42,707 --> 00:17:44,227
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">At least when I'm around,</font>

69
00:17:52,057 --> 00:17:54,567
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Not really, butâ€”</font>

70
00:18:14,027 --> 00:18:15,497
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah...</font>

71
00:18:25,447 --> 00:18:26,787
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Thank goodness.</font>

72
00:18:28,737 --> 00:18:29,777
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hey, Gin.</font>

73
00:18:34,107 --> 00:18:39,517
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">No matter what, don't ever touch me, okay?</font>

74
00:18:44,937 --> 00:18:45,607
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Okay?</font>

75
00:18:55,917 --> 00:18:57,177
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">No matter what!</font>

76
00:19:21,887 --> 00:19:23,607
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm leaving!</font>

77
00:19:26,317 --> 00:19:28,517
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin! I'm here again this year.</font>

78
00:19:36,517 --> 00:19:37,257
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Somehow,</font>

79
00:19:46,597 --> 00:19:47,357
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah.</font>

80
00:19:47,357 --> 00:19:48,047
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Huh?</i></font>

81
00:19:56,347 --> 00:19:57,437
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Oh.</font>

82
00:20:19,297 --> 00:20:23,617
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Gin ages much more slowly than humans.</i></font>

83
00:20:37,867 --> 00:20:39,397
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Here I go!</font>

84
00:21:13,807 --> 00:21:19,017
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>As the years go by, my appearance changes,</i></font>

85
00:21:20,487 --> 00:21:24,267
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>but Gin is almost the same as the day we met.</i></font>

86
00:22:37,067 --> 00:22:38,427
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Oh, Hotaru.</font>

87
00:22:38,427 --> 00:22:40,337
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I cut some watermelon. Let's eat.</font>

88
00:22:48,597 --> 00:22:49,607
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Where's Mom?</font>

89
00:23:00,457 --> 00:23:01,527
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I don't know,</font>

90
00:23:01,527 --> 00:23:04,267
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">but they said I'll still be here until the afternoon.</font>

91
00:23:05,367 --> 00:23:06,347
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is that so?</font>

92
00:23:09,187 --> 00:23:11,997
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">This summer's weather was good, so the watermelons are sweet.</font>

93
00:23:14,217 --> 00:23:17,407
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If it continues like this, then winter will be freezing.</font>

94
00:23:18,477 --> 00:23:19,757
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is it like that?</font>

95
00:23:20,687 --> 00:23:21,707
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's like that.</font>

96
00:23:24,577 --> 00:23:28,997
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Since this area's located between mountains and the ocean's far away,</font>

97
00:23:28,997 --> 00:23:31,917
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">the temperature difference between summer and winter is huge.</font>

98
00:23:32,617 --> 00:23:36,007
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">The cold of a winter that follows an especially hot summer</font>

99
00:23:36,387 --> 00:23:40,287
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">could probably freeze the mountain god himself.</font>

100
00:23:52,777 --> 00:23:53,787
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">A scarf?</font>

101
00:23:54,367 --> 00:23:55,027
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yep!</font>

102
00:23:55,537 --> 00:23:57,047
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Please use it in the winter, okay?</font>

103
00:24:03,177 --> 00:24:03,907
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Okay.</font>

104
00:24:06,457 --> 00:24:07,957
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">See you next year!</font>

105
00:24:23,867 --> 00:24:24,767
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Takegawa?</font>

106
00:24:25,397 --> 00:24:27,757
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Shouldn't you be heading to your next class soon?</font>

107
00:24:28,387 --> 00:24:30,077
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ah, you're right!</font>

108
00:24:30,077 --> 00:24:31,667
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Everyone left already.</font>

109
00:24:31,667 --> 00:24:33,217
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'll see you later.</font>

110
00:24:58,837 --> 00:25:00,187
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You're done?</font>

111
00:25:00,427 --> 00:25:03,657
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ah, you probably ate before dinner, didn't you?</font>

112
00:25:03,657 --> 00:25:05,407
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If you snack, you'll gain weight.</font>

113
00:25:05,407 --> 00:25:07,027
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I didn't eat anything!</font>

114
00:25:07,027 --> 00:25:08,897
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Jeez. I'm gonna take a bath!</font>

115
00:25:44,757 --> 00:25:46,497
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Oh, good morning.</font>

116
00:25:46,797 --> 00:25:47,537
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Good morning.</font>

117
00:25:47,887 --> 00:25:50,527
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">There, near your feet. It's frozen.</font>

118
00:26:02,127 --> 00:26:03,037
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Thank you.</font>

119
00:26:10,387 --> 00:26:12,127
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's cold today.</font>

120
00:26:23,057 --> 00:26:24,037
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>I want to</i></font>

121
00:26:26,197 --> 00:26:27,397
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>see Gin.</i></font>

122
00:26:52,937 --> 00:26:53,837
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>I want to</i></font>

123
00:27:26,897 --> 00:27:28,587
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is that your new uniform?</font>

124
00:27:29,027 --> 00:27:29,757
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah.</font>

125
00:27:39,527 --> 00:27:41,017
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Time really flies, doesn't it?</font>

126
00:27:41,627 --> 00:27:43,497
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You're already in high school, huh.</font>

127
00:27:43,497 --> 00:27:44,477
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yup.</font>

128
00:28:16,547 --> 00:28:19,717
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Then I can be with you more.</font>

129
00:28:21,227 --> 00:28:22,057
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">In autumn,</font>

130
00:28:29,047 --> 00:28:29,667
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Right?</font>

131
00:28:38,047 --> 00:28:40,897
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Let me tell you about myself.</font>

132
00:28:42,847 --> 00:28:44,437
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm not a spirit.</font>

133
00:28:45,457 --> 00:28:46,257
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">But,</font>

134
00:28:47,517 --> 00:28:48,997
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm no longer human.</font>

135
00:28:50,227 --> 00:28:52,177
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It seems like I was once a human,</font>

136
00:28:52,177 --> 00:28:53,797
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">but when I was a baby,</font>

137
00:28:53,797 --> 00:28:55,737
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I was abandoned in this forest.</font>

138
00:29:03,057 --> 00:29:06,447
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">as if to call back the parents who left me.</font>

139
00:29:56,747 --> 00:29:58,717
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's such a fragile thing.</font>

140
00:30:02,387 --> 00:30:03,997
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's just like snow, isn't it?</font>

141
00:30:05,107 --> 00:30:06,737
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin,</font>

142
00:30:07,867 --> 00:30:11,197
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I thought of you during winter.</font>

143
00:30:12,247 --> 00:30:13,097
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Even during autumn</font>

144
00:30:31,037 --> 00:30:31,517
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">But,</font>

145
00:30:32,577 --> 00:30:33,517
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">even still,</font>

146
00:30:42,847 --> 00:30:44,537
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Spirit festival?</font>

147
00:30:44,687 --> 00:30:47,857
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">No, a summer festival held by the spirits.</font>

148
00:30:48,087 --> 00:30:49,527
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">There's not much of a difference.</font>

149
00:30:49,527 --> 00:30:51,537
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">The nuance is completely different!</font>

150
00:30:58,797 --> 00:31:02,037
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">But tonight, can you sneak out of your house?</font>

151
00:31:02,587 --> 00:31:04,857
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I've wanted to go with you for a long time.</font>

152
00:31:06,977 --> 00:31:08,927
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I-I want to go!</font>

153
00:31:08,927 --> 00:31:11,717
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Meet me at eight at our usual place.</font>

154
00:31:12,217 --> 00:31:16,857
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">But a festival filled with spirits sounds a little unnerving...</font>

155
00:31:35,037 --> 00:31:35,997
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Do it.</font>

156
00:31:37,357 --> 00:31:38,307
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Seriously.</font>

157
00:31:55,517 --> 00:31:57,357
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Wait! Wait!</font>

158
00:32:21,967 --> 00:32:23,767
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Are they all disguised as humans?</font>

159
00:32:23,767 --> 00:32:25,907
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That's right. Impressive, isn't it?</font>

160
00:32:32,897 --> 00:32:33,707
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Who?</font>

161
00:32:40,127 --> 00:32:42,057
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Tie this around your wrist.</font>

162
00:32:42,527 --> 00:32:43,477
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You'll get lost.</font>

163
00:32:48,517 --> 00:32:50,427
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's just like going on a date!</font>

164
00:32:51,277 --> 00:32:53,027
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">This <i>is</i> a date.</font>

165
00:33:25,357 --> 00:33:26,237
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Here you go.</font>

166
00:33:46,247 --> 00:33:47,427
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Weird.</font>

167
00:34:00,087 --> 00:34:01,817
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ew, a couple!</font>

168
00:34:01,817 --> 00:34:03,217
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hey!</font>

169
00:34:15,067 --> 00:34:17,437
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Look! That kid has a tail!</font>

170
00:34:34,487 --> 00:34:36,427
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I-I'm sorry!</font>

171
00:34:56,867 --> 00:34:59,177
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Everyone went all out with their disguises, didn't they?</font>

172
00:34:59,177 --> 00:35:01,257
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It was like a mimicking competition!</font>

173
00:35:01,257 --> 00:35:02,677
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is it like this every year?</font>

174
00:35:46,787 --> 00:35:47,707
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That mask...</font>

175
00:35:48,617 --> 00:35:49,407
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Have it.</font>

176
00:35:56,117 --> 00:36:02,647
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>He probably won't come to that place next summer.</i></font>

177
00:36:05,077 --> 00:36:08,397
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>This is definitely our last...</i></font>

178
00:36:14,527 --> 00:36:15,657
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Are you okay?</font>

179
00:36:15,837 --> 00:36:17,627
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah. Thank you!</font>

180
00:36:18,297 --> 00:36:19,757
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Be careful, okay?</font>

181
00:36:29,447 --> 00:36:30,297
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin?</font>

182
00:36:33,337 --> 00:36:34,757
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Was that boy a human?</font>

183
00:36:41,417 --> 00:36:42,227
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin!</font>

184
00:36:43,127 --> 00:36:44,667
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Come here, Hotaru!</font>

185
00:37:28,047 --> 00:37:29,027
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I love you.</font>

186
00:37:29,777 --> 00:37:30,477
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah.</font>

187
00:37:31,647 --> 00:37:32,957
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I love you, too.</font>

188
00:37:55,407 --> 00:37:56,617
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Deep green.</i></font>

189
00:37:57,907 --> 00:37:59,687
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>This is the mountain god's forest.</i></font>

190
00:38:04,147 --> 00:38:06,837
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hotaru. Thank you.</font>

191
00:38:21,577 --> 00:38:23,897
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>I probably won't be able to</i></font>

192
00:38:31,747 --> 00:38:33,237
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>My tears will be overflowing.</i></font>

193
00:38:34,487 --> 00:38:42,987
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>But this warmth in my hands and these summer memories will live on in my heart.</i></font>

194
00:38:50,657 --> 00:38:52,447
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>So, let's go.</i></font>

195
00:38:57,337 --> 00:38:58,507
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Let us go.</i></font>

196
